<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hoderaiko lalandava Jeso Lay mpanavotro FFPM172</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hoderaiko lalandava
 Jeso Ilay Mpanavotro
 Noho ny fitiavana ahy,
 Maty mba ho soloko,
 Hoderaiko, hoderaiko,
 Fa ny rany masina
 Nentiny hanavotra ahy
 Afaka ny heloko.

[V2]
 Holazaiko lalandava
 Ny tantara mamiko,
 Izay nitadiavana ahy,
 Very noho ny heloko :
 Hoderaiko, ..sns.

[V3]
 Hohiraiko lalandava
 'Zao ny voninahiny
 Fa ny fahafatesana aza,
 Resy noho ny heriny ;
 Hoderaiko, ..sns.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>172</hymn_number>
<author>L. Mason</author>
</song>